name: Memory project 016
description:
Dolphin artifacts. 

This is based on the story in the Taiji. The Taiji dolphin drive hunt is based on driving dolphins and other small cetaceans into a small bay where they can be killed or captured for their meat and for sale to dolphinariums. Save dolphins! 

All photos are 8200 x 5000 pixels
